# P2 Findings

## P2-001 — Kimi circuit breaker needs cooldown / half-open state

### Area

`packages/thalamus/src/transports/llm-chat.ts`

### Current behavior

Kimi is skipped after 3 consecutive failures.

### Problem

There is no visible cooldown window or half-open retry. A temporary failure can cause the process to skip Kimi indefinitely.

### Required fix

Implement state:

```ts
type CircuitState = "closed" | "open" | "half_open";
```

Include:

* openedAt timestamp
* cooldownMs
* one half-open test call after cooldown
* reset on success

### Acceptance criteria

* Tests cover trip, cooldown, half-open success, half-open failure.

